*''The Four Sections - Music for Mallet Instruments, Voices, and Organ'', par le [[London Symphony Orchestra|London Symphony Orchestra]] dirigé par [[Michael Tilson Thomas|Michael Tilson Thomas]] et l'ensemble [[Steve Reich and Musicians|Steve Reich and Musicians]], [[Nonesuch Records|Nonesuch Records]], 1990.
